...remain the **exclusive property of Dylan Makori and Nomad Studios**.

### 3.2 Trademarks

The names "Nomad," "Nomad DAW," "Nomad Studios," and "Muse," along with associated logos and branding, are trademarks of Nomad Studios. You may not use these trademarks in any manner that suggests endorsement, affiliation, or sponsorship without prior written permission.

**Permitted:** "Built for Nomad DAW" (with attribution)  
**Not Permitted:** "Nomad Pro" or "MyDAW based on Nomad"

### 3.3 Attribution Requirements

If You reference, discuss, or use the Software in educational materials, blog posts, videos, or publications, You must:

- Clearly attribute the Software to "Dylan Makori / Nomad Studios"
- Include a link to the official repository: [NOMAD](https://github.com/currentsuspect/NOMAD)
- Do not imply endorsement without permission

